    "body":  "Enhance the document upload experience by refining the feedback shown during the upload and AI extraction process. These improvements aim to better communicate system status, reinforce trust in AI functionality, and improve overall UX.\n\n**Current Behavior:**\n\nDisplays spinner with:\n\n“Processing your document…\nExtracting qualifications using AI”\n\n**Requested Enhancements:**\n\n1. Progressive Messaging States\n\nShow contextual status updates as the process advances:\n\n- Start:\n\nUploading document…\n\n- Then:\n\nExtracting qualifications using AI…\n\n- Then:\n\nUpload complete. Preview below.\n\n_Implementation Tip: This can be a timed simulation or tied to actual backend states (if available)._\n\n**2. Visual Upgrade (Optional)**\n\n- Replace simple spinner with animated dots or \"AI-style\" visual cue.\n- Optional: Add shimmer, pulsing effect, or fun AI character to reinforce it\u0027s AI-powered.\n\n**3. Error Handling State**\n\nIf the upload or extraction fails, display:\n\n❌ Something went wrong while processing. Please try again or enter qualifications manually.\n\n**4. Success Confirmation**\n\nAfter successful extraction:\n\n✅ Qualifications extracted successfully! Ready to review and save.\n\n**Purpose:**\nThese enhancements are minor in code but high in impact. They create a clearer, more trustworthy experience that highlights the AI capabilities while giving the user confidence that the system is working as intended.",
